Orc records
You can learn where the Magic Orb originated from the Orc records. The Seer keeper who lives on the central island may have the records.
#subobj  1
Find the Seer keeper
The seer who keeps the records lives in the eastern end of the central island. But be cautious, he is well guarded!
#subobj  2
Get the record
You must kill the seer and take the record from his corpse.
